title: Tucker Carlson Faces Off with Berkeley Riots Backer Who Calls Milo Yiannopoulos a 'Fascist'
text:
Tucker Carlson Faces Off with Berkeley Riots Backer Who Calls Milo Yiannopoulos a 'Fascist'   
By Josh Feldman | Mediaite 
Tucker Carlson tonight faced off with Yvette Felarca, who was at Berkeley protesting Milo Yiannopoulos (where protests quickly turned into riots), who she considers to be a fascist.
